Rice is a grain that can be prepared in different ways. In a typical Nigerian party, if not served, the party is said to be poorly done. The conventional recipes served are cooked rice with tomato stew, jollof rice and fried rice. A different and easy way to prepare rice is with palm oil instead of the vegetable oil and tomatoes used for jollof rice and this is called the concoction rice. Here are the simple ingredients required. Concoction rice. Photo: My story time